{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"History: scrollRestoration property","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/scrollRestoration","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.History.scrollRestoration"],"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History_API\">History API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/length\"><code>length</code></a></li><li><em><code>scrollRestoration</code> </em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/state\"><code>state</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/back\"><code>back()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/forward\"><code>forward()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/go\"><code>go()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/pushState\"><code>pushState()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/replaceState\"><code>replaceState()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for History API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>scrollRestoration</code></strong> property of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a>\n  interface allows web applications to explicitly set default scroll restoration behavior\n  on history navigation.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>One of the following:</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"auto\"><a href=\"#auto\"><code>auto</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The location on the page to which the user has scrolled will be restored.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"manual\"><a href=\"#manual\"><code>manual</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      The location on the page is not restored. The user will have to scroll to the\n      location manually.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"query_the_current_scroll_restoration_behavior","title":"Query the current scroll restoration behavior","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> scrollRestoration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollRestoration<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scrollRestoration <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"manual\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"The location on the page is not restored, user will need to scroll manually.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"prevent_automatic_page_location_restoration","title":"Prevent automatic page location restoration","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollRestoration<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollRestoration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"manual\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-history-scroll-restoration-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.History.scrollRestoration"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.History.scrollRestoration"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The scrollRestoration property of History\n  interface allows web applications to explicitly set default scroll restoration behavior\n  on history navigation.","popularity":0.008,"modified":"2023-07-07T07:19:19.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/history/scrollrestoration","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/history/scrollrestoration/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/acfe8c9f1f4145f77653a2bc64a9744b001358dc","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"scrollRestoration","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History","title":"History"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History/scrollRestoration","title":"scrollRestoration"}],"pageTitle":"History: scrollRestoration property - Web APIs | MDN","no